              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/topics/architecture/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-arch">⬡</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Cloud Architecture</span>
