              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/topics/security/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-sec">🔒</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Security</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">IAM, zero-trust, compliance</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/topics/iac-kubernetes/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-iac">📦</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">IaC &amp; Kubernetes</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">Terraform, Helm, K8s, Ansible</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>

        <li class="has-dropdown">
          <a href="/runbooks/">Runbooks <span class="caret">▾</span></a>
          <ul class="nav-dropdown">
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/runbooks/aws/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-aws">☁</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">AWS Runbooks</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">Step-by-step operational playbooks</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/runbooks/deployment/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-devops">⚙</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Deployment Guides</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">End-to-end CI/CD walkthroughs</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/runbooks/architecture/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-arch">⬡</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Architecture Docs</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">Reference architectures &amp; ADRs</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/runbooks/security/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-sec">🔒</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Security Runbooks</span>
