              </span>
            </a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>

        <li class="has-dropdown">
          <a href="/interview/">Interview Prep <span class="caret">▾</span></a>
          <ul class="nav-dropdown">
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/interview/aws/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-aws">☁</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">AWS Q&amp;A</span>
