              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/interview/devops/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-devops">⚙</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">DevOps Q&amp;A</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">CI/CD, K8s, observability</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/interview/architect/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-arch">⬡</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">Principal Architect Q&amp;A</span>
                <span class="nav-dd-desc">Strategy, governance, leadership</span>
              </span>
            </a></li>
            <li><a class="nav-dd-item" href="/interview/system-design/">
              <span class="nav-dd-icon dd-iac">⚙</span>
              <span class="nav-dd-text">
                <span class="nav-dd-label">System Design</span>
